      "skillMarkdown": "# GIMP_GIMP_Configure_Themes_Preferences_and_Color_Management\n\n## When This Skill Applies\n\nUse this family for appearance-facing preference work:\n\n- switch the theme to a value that is visibly available in the live environment;\n- change adjacent appearance controls in the same Preferences surface;\n- verify that the requested theme selection actually took effect.\n\nDo not use this family for precision, gamma, ICC profile conversion, or advanced color-management changes. Those belong to `GIMP_GIMP_Manage_Image_Precision_Gamma_and_Color_Profiles`.\n\n## Result Verification Cues\n\n- The Preferences dialog is open on the appearance surface.\n- The requested theme value is visible in the live control and selected.\n- You never assume unsupported values such as a made-up theme that is not present in the dropdown.",
