          "whenNotToUse": "Do not use this card before any local edit has been attempted, when the canvas is showing transform handles or another active tool overlay, or when the task is about a global crop, resize, color adjustment, or any edit where the whole image should change. Ignore the save-related cue if the current task does not ask for a save step.",
