      "skillMarkdown": "# Create Calc Pivot Tables with Aggregations and Filters\n\n## When This Skill Applies\n\n- Use when the task explicitly asks for a pivot table or a data-pilot style summary.\n- Use when the work includes field layout, non-default aggregation, pivot filters, or renamed pivot output sheets.\n\n## Preconditions\n\n- The intended source table is selected or clearly identifiable.\n- The required row, column, filter, and value fields are known before finishing the pivot layout.\n\n## Procedure\n\n1. Use this card when the worksheet range is ready and Calc has opened the pivot-start dialog that asks how to use the selected source data.\n2. Use this card when the pivot layout is already in progress and a value field needs Average, Product, standard deviation, or another non-default summary function.\n3. Use this card when the pivot output needs to land on a newly named sheet and the Rename Sheet dialog is the next visible surface.\n4. Check that the pivot output is visible on the intended result sheet and that any task-specific filter or rename requirement is satisfied by live text, not by the example screenshot.\n\n## Visual State Card Usage\n\n- Detailed review cards live in `state_cards.json`.\n- Runtime-facing cards live in `runtime_state_cards.json`.\n- Load only the state whose screenshot actually matches the live Calc surface.\n- Image references in this package:\n  - `Images/finished_pivot_on_named_sheet.png`\n  - `Images/finished_pivot_on_named_sheet_before.png`\n  - `Images/finished_pivot_on_named_sheet_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_non_default_aggregation.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_non_default_aggregation_after.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_non_default_aggregation_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_select_source_dialog.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_select_source_dialog_after.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_select_source_dialog_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_sheet_rename_field.png`\n  - `Images/pivot_sheet_rename_field_focus_crop.png`\n\n## Common Failure Modes\n\n- Building the pivot from the wrong source or stale selection.\n- Leaving value fields on default Sum when the task required another aggregation.\n- Stopping in the layout dialog without checking the finished pivot output, rename, or filter state.",
