      "skillMarkdown": "# Insert and Structure Calc Charts\n\n## When This Skill Applies\n\n- Use when the task asks to insert a new chart, choose a chart family, or set up a chart from the current table.\n- Use when the main decision is chart structure rather than later legend or series styling.\n\n## Preconditions\n\n- The intended source table or selection is visible in Calc.\n- The requested chart type or target sheet is known before starting the wizard.\n\n## Procedure\n\n1. Use when the task asks to insert a new chart, choose a chart family, or set up a chart from the current table.\n2. The chart family and data source must be established first.\n3. Check the final visible Calc state and confirm the task-specific result is actually present.\n\n## Visual State Card Usage\n\n- Detailed review cards live in `state_cards.json`.\n- Runtime-facing cards live in `runtime_state_cards.json`.\n- Load only the state whose screenshot actually matches the live Calc surface.\n- Image references in this package:\n  - `Images/chart_data_series_in_rows.png`\n  - `Images/chart_data_series_in_rows_after.png`\n  - `Images/chart_data_series_in_rows_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/combo_chart_number_of_lines.png`\n  - `Images/combo_chart_number_of_lines_after.png`\n  - `Images/combo_chart_number_of_lines_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/finished_3d_pyramid_chart.png`\n  - `Images/finished_3d_pyramid_chart_before.png`\n  - `Images/finished_3d_pyramid_chart_focus_crop.png`\n  - `Images/pyramid_shape_in_chart_type.png`\n  - `Images/pyramid_shape_in_chart_type_focus_crop.png`\n\n## Common Failure Modes\n\n- Starting a chart from the wrong source range or wrong sheet.\n- Treating later legend or axis formatting as part of the initial insertion flow.",
