      "skillMarkdown": "# Adjust Text Bullets, Indentation, Strikethrough, and Alignment\n\n## When This Skill Applies\n\nUse this skill for paragraph-level edits on existing slide text: bullets, numbering, indentation, alignment, line spacing, or strikeout.\n\nDo not use it as the main path for font family, text color, highlight, or other pure Character edits.\n\n## Core Procedure\n\n1. Select the exact paragraph or TOC line.\n2. Open the paragraph/list control family that matches the request.\n3. Apply the requested paragraph or strikeout change.\n4. Verify the same line on the canvas before leaving it.\n\n## Result Verification Cues\n\n- The same line that was selected must show the requested paragraph result.\n- A menu opening or checkbox toggling is not enough without the on-canvas line change.\n- For multi-line tasks, repeat the same local check for each target line.",
