          "whenNotToUse": "Do not use this card once an object has already been inserted or selected on the slide, when the UI is focused on resizing or formatting an existing object, or when the screenshot does not show the Insert dropdown itself. It is also a poor match if the workflow starts from a toolbar shortcut or sidebar-only control instead of the Insert menu.",
