          "whenNotToUse": "Do not use if the task is only editing text, objects, notes, backgrounds, or save/export settings on the current slide, if you are dragging thumbnails to reorder slides, or if only the right sidebar layouts are visible without a thumbnail context menu anchored to the intended slide.",
